Package: phevmicrosimr
Type: Package
Title: Simulates ZEV adoption in Ireland 2015-2050
Version: 2.0.0
Author: Joe Wheatley
Maintainer: The package maintainer <joe.wheatley@ucd.ie>
Description: Agent-based micro-simulation of ZEV adoption based on detailed policy and technology scenarios.This packages contains functions to load a run a pre-calibrated model. Functions to handle policy scenarios are in policy.R. Functions to deal with market scenarios are in market.R. Functions to deal with BEV technology are in technology.R. Good luck!
License: Apache License (>= 2.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    tibble,
    magrittr,
    tidygraph,
    tidyverse,
    lubridate,
    ggplot2,
    data.table,
    ggthemes,
    igraph,latex2exp,
    tidyr,
    foreach,
    doParallel,
    cluster
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
